    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让霓虹灯光在你的骨髓里跳动吧！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想不想用一种激动人心的全新方式体验你最爱的音乐风格？《滚动的彩带》（BandRoll）将有趣的游戏和华丽的视觉效果完美结合，让你在听自己喜欢的歌曲时，尽情享受游戏的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/184f1c07779c76348e4e40347a2e4e58.poster.avif?t=1763473832\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/184f1c07779c76348e4e40347a2e4e58.webm?t=1763473832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/184f1c07779c76348e4e40347a2e4e58.mp4?t=1763473832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多种难度选择</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在正确的时机于平台间滑动，得到高分，通过一个个关卡。每个关卡都有独特的速度和挑战。如果你不满足于简单的关卡，那你一定会在更难的关卡那得到满足。在每一次尝试中，吸取教训，提高分数！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏方法简单</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你只需要按WASD或者方向键，你可以在平台间上下左右移动。有些平台会要求你按住按键不要松开。简单吧，但要记住，简单并不意味着容易。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>竞争</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过一关后，与其他人的分数一较高下。不要为自己不是第一名而烦恼，你可以重玩已经通关的每个关卡，以获得更高的分数。要提高你的总分，你得先确保自己完成了所有的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>不同的球</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通关就能获得金币，你可以用金币购买和使用不同种类的球</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/af3ea3a6d76ee3cd3fff693ce01e401a.poster.avif?t=1763473832\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/af3ea3a6d76ee3cd3fff693ce01e401a.webm?t=1763473832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/af3ea3a6d76ee3cd3fff693ce01e401a.mp4?t=1763473832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>每个风格的音乐都有独特的霓虹宇宙</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着音乐风格的改变，动态宇宙系统会发生变化，去体验不同的霓虹宇宙吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >电音飞扬</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >摇滚浪潮</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >金属狂热</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >浪漫古典</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/e68c3dcfb83f263a486e716348506e19.poster.avif?t=1763473832\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/e68c3dcfb83f263a486e716348506e19.webm?t=1763473832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2206390/extras/e68c3dcfb83f263a486e716348506e19.mp4?t=1763473832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关卡编辑（敬请期待）</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你最喜欢的歌曲放入游戏中，然后使用菜单中的关卡编辑器进行游戏。在Steam创意工坊中分享您的自定义关卡，或下载体验其他玩家制作的自定义关卡</p>",
